An array of text prompts to use for generation.

Given a text prompt with the text `A lighthouse on a cliff` and a weight of `0.5`, it would be represented as:

```
"text_prompts": [
  {
    "text": "A lighthouse on a cliff",
    "weight": 0.5
  }
]
```
